    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="uva_jc.00456_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">431 Stevens <choice><abbr>st</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice> Camden</name>
                    <date when="1877-02-13" rend="right"><choice><abbr>Feb</abbr><expan>February</expan></choice> 13&#8212;p m</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear John Burroughs</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Yours of 6th only <choice><abbr>rec'd</abbr><expan>received</expan></choice> this afternoon by me&#8212;as I have just <choice><abbr>return'd</abbr><expan>returned</expan></choice> <choice><orig>to day</orig><reg>today</reg></choice> from a week down at a farm in Jersey&#8212;</p>
           
            <p>&#8212;I hope you will adopt <hi rend="underline">Birds &#38; Poets</hi>&#8212;&#38; then the <hi rend="underline">Flight of the Eagle</hi><ptr target="uva.00382_n1"/>&#8212;As the more I think of them, the better I like both&#8212;(I mean directly &#38; indirectly, &#38; for wear)&#8212;Come on to Mrs. Gilchrist's 16th or 17th<ptr target="uva.00382_n2"/>&#8212;I will prepare them&#8212;I will be there&#8212;it is 1929 north 22d street&#8212;I still keep pretty well for me</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">WW</signed>
            </closer>
